#: tfrmcodefilter.frmlaunchbranchmapper.hint
msgid ""
"Starts a single stepping (branch only) trace and records all unique IP's encountered.  You can use the results from this with the \"From File\" address list\n"
"Make sure that the code you're interested in is executed at least once\n"
"\n"
"<WARNING: SLOW and recommended as last resort>"
