"\n"
"<警告:速度很慢,建议作为最后手段>"

#: tfrmcodefilter.groupbox1.caption
msgid "Load address list"
msgstr "加载地址列表"

#: tfrmcodefilter.label1.caption
msgid ""
"This will place software breakpoints(0xcc) on many locations of interest (Usually CALLs) and then track which ones get executed and which ones do not.\n"
"By specifying that some code has been executed and some not you can filter down the list till it's only ones you're interested in"
msgstr ""
"这将在许多感兴趣的位置(通常是CALL指令)放置软件断点(0xcc),然后跟踪哪些被执行,哪些没有。\n"
"通过指定某些代码已执行而某些未执行,你可以过滤列表直到只剩下你感兴趣的部分"

