#: tfrmpointerscannersettings.btnok.caption
msgctxt "tfrmpointerscannersettings.btnok.caption"
msgid "OK"
msgstr "确定"

#: tfrmpointerscannersettings.caption
msgid "Pointerscanner scanoptions"
msgstr "\"指针扫描器\"选项"

#: tfrmpointerscannersettings.cbacceptnonmodulevtable.caption
msgid "Also accept non-module addresses"
msgstr "同时接受非模块地址"

#: tfrmpointerscannersettings.cballigned.caption
msgid "Addresses must be 32-bit alligned"
msgstr "地址必须是32位(4字节对齐)的"

#: tfrmpointerscannersettings.cballigned.hint
msgid ""
"When enabled, only pointers that are stored in an address dividable by 4 are looked at\n"
"When disabled, it won't bother.\n"
"\n"
"pro: Fast scans\n"
"Con: On some horrible designed games that you shouldn't even play it won't find the paths"
msgstr "启用时，仅查看存储在可被 4 整除的地址中的指针\n禁用时，不做此限制。\n\n优点：快速扫描\n缺点：在一些设计糟糕你不该玩的游戏中找不到路径"

#: tfrmpointerscannersettings.cballowruntimeworkers.caption
msgid "Allow scanners to connect at runtime"
msgstr "允许扫描器在运行时连接"

#: tfrmpointerscannersettings.cballowruntimeworkers.hint
msgctxt "tfrmpointerscannersettings.cballowruntimeworkers.hint"
msgid "Opens a port that other systems running the pointerscanner can connect to and help out with the scan"
msgstr "打开一个端口运行 pointerscanner 时其他系统可以连接并参与扫描"

#: tfrmpointerscannersettings.cbbenchmark.caption
msgid "Benchmark system"
msgstr "基准测试系统"

#: tfrmpointerscannersettings.cbclasspointersonly.caption
msgid "First element of pointerstruct must point to module (e.g vtable)"
msgstr "指针结构的第一个元素必须指向模块(例如虚拟表)"

#: tfrmpointerscannersettings.cbclasspointersonly.hint
msgid ""
"Object oriented programming languages tend to implement classobjects by having a pointer in the first element to something that describes the class\n"
"With this option enabled, ce will check if it's a classobject by checking that rule. If not, it won't see it as a pointer.\n"
"pro:Tremendous speed increase and almost perfect pointers\n"
"con:Doesn't work with runtime generated classes (java, .net) "
msgstr "面向对象编程语言倾向于通过在第一个元素中放置一个指向描述类的内容的指针来实现类对象\n启用此选项后，CE 将通过检查该规则来判断是否为类对象。如果不是，则不会将其视为指针。\n优点：极大的速度提升和几乎完美的指针\n缺点：不适用于运行时生成的类（java、.net）"

#: tfrmpointerscannersettings.cbcomparetootherpointermaps.caption
msgid "Compare results with other saved pointermap(s)"
msgstr "与其它保存的\"指针映射集\"结果相比对"

#: tfrmpointerscannersettings.cbcomparetootherpointermaps.hint
msgid ""
"When ticked you can add other pointermaps which will be used to verify that the pointers it finds are correct. You will have to fill in the correct address for each pointermap you provide.\n"
"Note: expect at least the size of the game itself in memory for every pointermap used\n"
msgstr "勾选后，你可以添加其他指针图用于验证找到的指针是否正确。你需要为每个提供的指针图填入正确的地址。\n注意：每个使用的指针图预计至少需要游戏本身在内存中的大小\n"

#: tfrmpointerscannersettings.cbcompressedpointerscanfile.caption
msgid "Compressed pointerscan file"
msgstr "压缩\"指针扫描\"(.PTR)文件"

#: tfrmpointerscannersettings.cbcompressedpointerscanfile.hint
msgid ""
"Compresses the generated .PTR files slightly so they take less space on the disk and less time writing to disk.\n"
"Most of the time the bottleneck of a pointerscan is disk writing, so it is recommended to use this option.\n"
"\n"
"Compressed .PTR files can not be read out by older Cheat Engine versions"
msgstr "稍微压缩生成的 .PTR 文件，使其占用更少的磁盘空间和更少的写入时间。\n大多数情况下指针扫描的瓶颈是磁盘写入，因此建议使用此选项。\n\n压缩的 .PTR 文件无法被旧版本的 Cheat Engine 读取"

#: tfrmpointerscannersettings.cbconnecttonode.caption
msgid "Connect to pointerscan node"
msgstr "连接到\"指针扫描器\"节点"

#: tfrmpointerscannersettings.cbconnecttonode.hint
msgctxt "tfrmpointerscannersettings.cbconnecttonode.hint"
msgid ""
"When checked will send a broadcast message on the local network which will tell pointer scanner systems to join this scan if they are set to auto join\n"
"\n"
"You can use \"Setup specific IP's to notify\" to notify systems of this scan that are outside of the local network"
msgstr "勾选后将在本地网络上发送广播消息，通知设置为自动加入的指针扫描系统加入此扫描\n\n你可以使用"设置特定 IP 通知"来通知本地网络之外的系统加入此扫描"

#: tfrmpointerscannersettings.cbheaponly.caption
msgid "Only allow static and heap addresses in the path"
msgstr "仅允许静态地址/堆地址在路径中"

#: tfrmpointerscannersettings.cbheaponly.hint
msgid "If the address you search for isn't a heap address, the scan will return 0 results"
msgstr "如果你要搜索的地址并不是堆地址, 扫描后会返回0结果"

#: tfrmpointerscannersettings.cbignoreupperbyte.caption
msgid "Ignore upper byte of pointers"
msgstr "忽略指针的高字节"

#: tfrmpointerscannersettings.cbincludesystemmodules.caption
msgctxt "tfrmpointerscannersettings.cbincludesystemmodules.caption"
msgid "Include system modules"
msgstr "包括系统模块"

#: tfrmpointerscannersettings.cblimitscantoregionfile.caption
msgctxt "tfrmpointerscannersettings.cblimitscantoregionfile.caption"
msgid "Limit scan to specified region file"
msgstr "限制扫描指定的内存区域的文件"

#: tfrmpointerscannersettings.cbmaxoffsetspernode.caption
msgid "Max different offsets per node:"
msgstr "每个节点的偏移最大相差:"

#: tfrmpointerscannersettings.cbmaxoffsetspernode.hint
msgid ""
"When the pointerscan looks through the list of pointers with a specific value, it goes through every single pointer that has that value. Every time increasing the offset slightly.\n"
"With this feature enabled the pointerscan will only check the first few pointers with that value.\n"
"\n"
"pro: Extremely fast, and the results have the lowest pointer paths possible.\n"
"con: You'll miss a lot of pointers that might be valid too "
msgstr "当指针扫描查看具有特定数值的指针列表时，它会遍历每一个具有该数值的指针，每次稍微增加偏移。\n启用此功能后，指针扫描将只检查具有该数值的前几个指针。\n\n优点：极快，结果具有最低可能的指针路径。\n缺点：你可能会错过很多也可能有效的指针"

#: tfrmpointerscannersettings.cbmustendwithspecificoffset.caption
msgid "Pointers must end with specific offsets"
msgstr "指针必须以特定的偏移结束"

#: tfrmpointerscannersettings.cbmuststartwithbase.caption
msgid "Base address must be in specific range"
msgstr "基础地址必须在指定范围内"

#: tfrmpointerscannersettings.cbmuststartwithbase.hint
msgid ""
"Will only mark the given range as valid base address (Will reduce the number of results)\n"
"This internally makes use of the \"Only find paths with a static address\" feature by marking the provided range as static only, so it must be enabled."
msgstr "仅将给定范围标记为有效基地址（将减少结果数量）\n这在内部使用"仅查找具有静态地址的路径"功能，通过将提供的范围标记为仅静态，因此必须启用该功能。"

#: tfrmpointerscannersettings.cbnegativeoffsets.caption
msgid "Also scan for negative offsets"
msgstr "同时扫描负偏移"

#: tfrmpointerscannersettings.cbnegativeoffsets.hint
msgid ""
"Let's you scan for negative offsets\n"
"Can not be used in combination with compressed pointerscan files"
msgstr ""
"让你扫描负偏移\n"
"不能与压缩的指针扫描文件一起使用"

#: tfrmpointerscannersettings.cbnoloop.caption
msgid "No looping pointers"
msgstr "无循环指针"

#: tfrmpointerscannersettings.cbnoloop.hint
msgid ""
"This will filter out pointerpaths that ended up in a loop\n"
"e.g:\n"
"base->p1->p2->p3->p1->p4\n"
"\n"
"you could just as well do base->p1->p4 then, so throw this one away (base->p1->p4 will be found another way)\n"
"\n"
"pro: Less results so less diskspace used\n"
"con: slightly slows down the scan as it needs to check for loops every single iteration "
msgstr "这将过滤掉最终进入循环的指针路径\n例如：\nbase->p1->p2->p3->p1->p4\n\n你同样可以直接 base->p1->p4，所以丢弃这个（base->p1->p4 会通过其他方式找到）\n\n优点：结果更少，磁盘空间使用更少\n缺点：略微减慢扫描速度，因为每次迭代都需要检查循环"

#: tfrmpointerscannersettings.cbnoreadonly.caption
msgid "Don't include pointers with read-only nodes"
msgstr "不包括只读节点的指针"

#: tfrmpointerscannersettings.cbnoreadonly.hint
msgid ""
"When checked the pointerscan will throw away memory that is readonly. So when it looks for paths, it won't encounter paths that pass through read only memory blocks.\n"
"\n"
"When it's unchecked, it does include readonly memory\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"pro: faster, less useless results\n"
"con: If the game decides to mark a pointer as readonly ce won't find it "
msgstr "勾选后，指针扫描将丢弃只读内存。因此在查找路径时，不会遇到通过只读内存块的路径。\n\n未勾选时，会包含只读内存\n\n\n优点：更快，无用结果更少\n缺点：如果游戏决定将指针标记为只读，CE 将找不到它"

#: tfrmpointerscannersettings.cbonlyonestatic.caption
msgid "Stop traversing a path when a static has been found"
msgstr "找到一个静态的就停止遍历路径"

#: tfrmpointerscannersettings.cbonlyonestatic.hint
msgid ""
"When the pointerscanner goes through the list of pointervalues with a specific value, this will stop exploring other paths as soon as it encounters a static pointer to that value\n"
"\n"
"pro: Fast\n"
"con: You may miss some valid results "
msgstr "当指针扫描器遍历具有特定数值的指针数值列表时，一旦遇到指向该数值的静态指针，就会停止探索其他路径\n\n优点：快速\n缺点：你可能会错过一些有效的结果"

#: tfrmpointerscannersettings.cbscanresidentmemory.caption
msgid "Only scan resident memory"
msgstr "仅扫描驻留内存"

#: tfrmpointerscannersettings.cbscanresidentmemory.hint
msgid "Skip paged out memory pages"
msgstr "跳过已分页出的内存页"

#: tfrmpointerscannersettings.cbshowadvancedoptions.caption
msgid "Show advanced options"
msgstr "显示高级选项"

#: tfrmpointerscannersettings.cbstackonly.caption
msgid "Stack addresses as ONLY static address"
msgstr "堆栈地址视为仅有静态地址"

#: tfrmpointerscannersettings.cbstackonly.hint
msgid ""
"Enable this if you wish to only find pointer paths with a stack address.\n"
"Combine this with \"Only find paths with a static address\" (default on) else this option will have no effect\n"
"\n"
"pro: You'll only get paths from the stack\n"
"con: You don't get paths from random dll's or the .exe "
msgstr "如果你希望仅查找具有栈地址的指针路径，请启用此选项。\n将此与"仅查找具有静态地址的路径"（默认开启）结合使用，否则此选项无效\n\n优点：你只会得到来自栈的路径\n缺点：你不会得到来自随机 dll 或 .exe 的路径"

#: tfrmpointerscannersettings.cbstaticonly.caption
msgid "Only find paths with a static address"
msgstr "只查找静态地址的路径"

#: tfrmpointerscannersettings.cbstaticonly.hint
msgid ""
"When checked the pointerscan will only store a path when it starts with a static address. (or easily looked up address)\n"
"When it's disabled, it finds every single pointer path\n"
"\n"
"pro: Fast\n"
"con: It may miss pointers that are accessed by special paths like thread local storage. (but even then they'd be useless for ce as they will change)"
msgstr "勾选后，指针扫描仅在路径以静态地址（或易于查找的地址）开头时才存储路径。\n禁用时，会查找每一个指针路径\n\n优点：快速\n缺点：可能会错过通过线程本地存储等特殊路径访问的指针。（但即便如此，它们对 CE 也是无用的，因为它们会变化）"

#: tfrmpointerscannersettings.cbstaticstacks.caption
msgid "Allow stack addresses of the first thread(s) to be handled as static"
msgstr "允许第一个线程的堆栈地址视为静态处理"

#: tfrmpointerscannersettings.cbstaticstacks.hint
msgid ""
"This allows the stack of threads to be seen as static addresses by the pointerscan.\n"
"The main thread is always a sure bet that it's the first one in the list. And often the second thread created is pretty stable as well.\n"
"With more there's a bigger change they get created and destroyed randomly\n"
"\n"
"When a program enters a function and exits it, the stack pointer decreases and increases, and the data there gets written to.\n"
"The farther the game is inside function calls, the more static the older data will be.\n"
"\n"
"With max stack offset: you can set the max size that can be deemed as static enough.\n"
"\n"
"pro: It finds paths otherwise never found\n"
"con: More results, more diskspace "
msgstr "这允许指针扫描将线程的栈视为静态地址。\n主线程几乎肯定是列表中的第一个。通常第二个创建的线程也相当稳定。\n更多的线程被随机创建和销毁的可能性更大\n\n当程序进入和退出函数时，栈指针会减少和增加，那里的数据会被写入。\n游戏在函数调用中越深，旧数据就越静态。\n\n通过最大栈偏移：你可以设置可被视为足够静态的最大大小。\n\n优点：能找到其他方式找不到的路径\n缺点：更多结果，更多磁盘空间"

#: tfrmpointerscannersettings.cbuseheapdata.caption
msgid "Improve pointerscan with gathered heap data"
msgstr "采集堆(数据)以便改善\"指针扫描\"性能"

#: tfrmpointerscannersettings.cbuseheapdata.hint
msgid ""
"When this is checked the heap is used to figure out the offset sizes, instead of blindly guessing them.\n"
"pro: Greatly improve speed and a lot less useless results\n"
"con: if the game allocates gigantic chunks of heap memory, and then divides it up itself, this will give wrong results.\n"
"\n"
"In other cases this will give perfect pointers "
msgstr "勾选此项后，将使用堆来确定偏移大小，而不是盲目猜测。\n优点：大幅提高速度并减少无用结果\n缺点：如果游戏分配了巨大的堆内存块然后自行分割，这将给出错误结果。\n\n在其他情况下，这将给出完美的指针"

#: tfrmpointerscannersettings.cbuseloadedpointermap.caption
msgctxt "tfrmpointerscannersettings.cbuseloadedpointermap.caption"
msgid "Use saved pointermap"
msgstr "使用保存的\"指针映射集\""

#: tfrmpointerscannersettings.cbuseloadedpointermap.hint
msgid ""
"Use this if you have created a pointermap on a system that runs the game, but you wish to do the scan on another system (or multiple systems).\n"
"Checking this option will open a dialog where you can select the pointermap"
msgstr "如果你在运行游戏的系统上创建了指针图，但希望在另一个系统（或多个系统）上进行扫描，请使用此选项。\n勾选此选项将打开一个对话框，你可以在其中选择指针图"

