#: tfrmsetuppsnnode.cballowtempfiles.caption
msgid "Allow temp file usage"
msgstr "允许使用临时文件"

#: tfrmsetuppsnnode.cballowtempfiles.hint
msgid ""
"When checked it will save the scandata files it receives into temporary files on the harddisk\n"
"If it's unchecked these files will stay in memory in their original file format as well as their extracted format\n"
"\n"
"This can be useful when on a system with no disk access but lots of RAM"
msgstr "勾选后，会将接收到的扫描数据文件保存到硬盘上的临时文件中\n未勾选时，这些文件将以原始文件格式和解压格式保留在内存中\n\n这在没有磁盘访问但有大量 RAM 的系统上很有用"

#: tfrmsetuppsnnode.cbautotrustchildren.caption
msgid "Automatically trust stability of all new childnodes"
msgstr "自动信任所有新子节点的稳定性"

#: tfrmsetuppsnnode.cbautotrustchildren.hint
msgid ""
"Normally when a worker terminates before the scan is done it will send all it's paths to it's connected node and then close, but if the system would crash it wouldn't be able to send it's queues to the node, causing in a loss of possible paths to examine\n"
"\n"
"When unchecked the owning controller/scanner will only send it one pointerpath queue element at a time and remembers that queue element until the worker reports that it has 0 queue elements, meaning it successfully completed the work item.\n"
"Also note that under normal circumstaces the node will accept new paths from the worker, but in the case of non stable workers this is not done and the worker has to do all the sub paths it generated itself\n"
"\n"
"In the node screen you will be able to change the state of a worker"
msgstr "通常当工作节点在扫描完成前终止时，它会将其所有路径发送到连接的节点然后关闭，但如果系统崩溃，它将无法将其队列发送到节点，导致可能丢失待检查的路径\n\n未勾选时，所属控制器/扫描器每次只发送一个指针路径队列元素，并记住该队列元素直到工作节点报告它有 0 个队列元素，意味着它成功完成了工作项。\n还要注意，在正常情况下节点会接受来自工作节点的新路径，但在非稳定工作节点的情况下不会这样做，工作节点必须自己完成它生成的所有子路径\n\n在节点屏幕中你将能够更改工作节点的状态"

#: tfrmsetuppsnnode.cbconnecttoothernode.caption
msgid "Connect to other node as"
msgstr "连接到其它节点"

#: tfrmsetuppsnnode.cbconnecttoothernode.hint
msgid "Connect to another system as it's parent or child"
msgstr "连接到另一个系统的父节点或子节点"

#: tfrmsetuppsnnode.cbmaxfoundresults.caption
msgid "Stop scans after finding max amount of results"
msgstr "找到的结果数达到允许的最大数量后就停止扫描"

#: tfrmsetuppsnnode.cbmaxfoundresults.hint
msgid ""
"This will terminate all the children and disconnect from the parent after having found at least the given amount of results\n"
"It's slightly innacurate as the check is only done every 10 seconds or so\n"
"\n"
"Note: This only has effect when there is at least one parent in the queue. Otherwise it's not going to disconnect"
msgstr "这将在找到至少给定数量的结果后终止所有子进程并断开与父节点的连接\n略有不准，因为检查大约每 10 秒才进行一次\n\n注意：这仅在队列中至少有一个父节点时才有效。否则不会断开连接"

#: tfrmsetuppsnnode.cbmaxtimetoscan.caption
msgid "Stop scans after specific time"
msgstr "在特定时间后停止扫描"

#: tfrmsetuppsnnode.cbmaxtimetoscan.hint
msgid ""
"This will terminate all the children and disconnect from the parent after scanning for the given amount of time.\n"
"\n"
"Note: This only has effect when there is at least one parent in the queue. Otherwise it's not going to disconnect"
msgstr "这将在扫描给定时间后终止所有子进程并断开与父节点的连接。\n\n注意：这仅在队列中至少有一个父节点时才有效。否则不会断开连接"

