msgstr "初始启动后不处理新线程"

#: tfrmultimap2.cbkernelmode.caption
msgid "Kernelmode"
msgstr "内核模式"

#: tfrmultimap2.cbnointerrupts.caption
msgid "Do not trigger interrupts when full"
msgstr "满时不触发中断"

#: tfrmultimap2.cbnointerrupts.hint
msgid ""
"In Windows 10, when a PMI triggers, it will BSOD with \"PROFILER_CONFIGURATION_ILLEGAL\" if you use ranges and don't have a kernelmode debugger attached\n"
"\n"
"Tip: Use a huge buffer and autoprocess/flush the tracefiles\n"
"Tip2: If DBVM is running it will hide the fact that regions are used from windows, and this you can just use interrupts like before"
msgstr ""
"在 Windows 10 中，当 PMI 触发时，如果使用范围且没有附加内核模式调试器，将会出现\"PROFILER_CONFIGURATION_ILLEGAL\"蓝屏\n"
"\n"
"提示：使用大缓冲区并自动处理/刷新跟踪文件\n"
"提示2：如果 DBVM 正在运行，它会对 Windows 隐藏正在使用区域的事实，这样你就可以像以前一样使用中断"

#: tfrmultimap2.cbparsetotextfile.caption
msgid "Parse trace to textfile"
msgstr "将跟踪解析到文本文件"

#: tfrmultimap2.cbparsetotextfile.hint
msgid ""
"When enabled will write the sequence of events as they happen as plain text to a file called cpu#trace.txt.\n"
"This file contains the disassemble and some event data that happens along the way.\n"
"\n"
"It is recommended to use a very small range, and a stop condition"
msgstr "启用后，将事件发生的序列以纯文本形式写入名为 cpu#trace.txt 的文件。\n此文件包含反汇编和过程中发生的一些事件数据。\n\n建议使用非常小的范围和停止条件"

